"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-28-Olympics-2024-Bach-applauds-China-for-history-making-cloud-AI-tech-1vBvpAVXW5G-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  The Chinese delegation members attend the opening ceremony of the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France, July 26, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9392347153630096, \"rank\": 0.06469526917469022, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999851575013, \"rank\": 1.4842311975923825e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995162018460383, \"rank\": 0.00030556673460692337, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Cloud technology has surpassed satellite for the first time to become the main way to broadcast the Olympic Games, increasing broadcasting speeds at a lower cost.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics, the Olympic Broadcasting Services (OBS) OBS and Alibaba Cloud, the cloud computing arm of China's internet giant Alibaba, co-developed the OBS Cloud 3.0 forthe opening ceremony of the Games.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Broadcasting Services\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}, {\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999999802185, \"rank\": 1.9748958798238993e-11, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999992800874542, \"rank\": 7.199131319302915e-07, \"text\": \"Alibaba Cloud\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9998983429344653, \"rank\": 0.0001003919124970336, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999997046416, \"rank\": 2.9534897720214246e-10, \"text\": \"Alibaba\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999999802185, \"rank\": 1.9748958798238993e-11, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC) President Thomas Bach attended the official opening of Alibaba Wonder Avenue on Saturday, hailing the impact that Alibaba's AI expertise is already having on the Olympic Movement.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999997046416, \"rank\": 2.9534897720214246e-10, \"text\": \"Alibaba\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999997046416, \"rank\": 2.9534897720214246e-10, \"text\": \"Alibaba\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999808324, \"rank\": 1.9173911361542157e-10, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999140991413762, \"rank\": 8.590823814096004e-05, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Alibaba's Wonder Avenue is the latest example of how our partnership is taking the Olympic Movement into the digital age,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999140991413762, \"rank\": 8.590823814096004e-05, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Alibaba plays an essential role when it comes to supporting technology during the Olympic Games, greatly increasing the efficiency and sustainability of Olympic Games operations.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our partnership also extends beyond the Olympic Games, with Alibaba playing a defining role in our Olympic AI Agenda, helping us harness the great potential of AI in a responsible way.\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999997046416, \"rank\": 2.9534897720214246e-10, \"text\": \"Alibaba\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999808324, \"rank\": 1.9173911361542157e-10, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All these examples highlight how Alibaba is the perfect partner when it comes to shaping our digital future.\\\"\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999997046416, \"rank\": 2.9534897720214246e-10, \"text\": \"Alibaba\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, a total of 11,000 hours of competitive live-feeds are expected to be distributed via OBS Cloud to over 200 countries and regions around the world.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999999802185, \"rank\": 1.9748958798238993e-11, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The OBS has installed multi-camera replay systems in 14 venues to provide frame-freeze slow-motion replays for sports like rugby, table tennis, athletics, skateboarding and other events.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999999802185, \"rank\": 1.9748958798238993e-11, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other technologies, including AI, were also utilized in 14 venues to give global viewers a more immersive experience of the games.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1943, \"end\": 1945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999808324, \"rank\": 1.9173911361542157e-10, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IOC President Thomas Bach speaks ahead of the opening ceremony of the 2024 Summer Olympic Games in Paris, France, July 26, 2024.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999851575013, \"rank\": 1.4842311975923825e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995162018460383, \"rank\": 0.00030556673460692337, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Yiannis Exarchos, CEO of Olympic Broadcasting Services, told CGTN that \\\"One of the things that we are doing with Alibaba, which I think is fascinating, and you will see in the Games of Paris, is that we will be generating 360 degree replay.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exarch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4111604217550052e-16, \"text\": \"Exarchos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exarch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exarch\"}, {\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Broadcasting Services\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}, {\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"score\": 0.9999999997046416, \"rank\": 2.9534897720214246e-10, \"text\": \"Alibaba\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alibaba_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 2365, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999851575013, \"rank\": 1.4842311975923825e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we will freeze at some moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will be able to go all around the athlete.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is important, not just because it's very interesting visually, but also because it allows the viewers to better understand what the athletes are actually doing, to understand and appreciate what is the level of athleticism that is required to become an Olympic athlete.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And also, it helps audiences and especially younger generations, better understand the sport,\\\" the CEO added.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Cloud is extremely important for a major event like the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cloud is all about scalability, how you can grow an infrastructure in a very easy and efficient manner.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And this is certainly something that is required for a broadcast event like covering the Olympic Games, where it's really all about size,\\\" said Sotiris Salamouris, chief technology officer of OBS.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999999802185, \"rank\": 1.9748958798238993e-11, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have so much broadcast to do and there is so much time available and resources available in a short period of time, that cloud really give us the option to use this kind of infrastructure, establish it in a very, very small period of time, make it used only while it is used, so essentially for the two weeks of the Games, and then take it down after the Games are over.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's a service that fits very well in the profile of technology use during the Olympic Games,\\\" Sotiris Salamouris added.\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 4019, \"entities\": []}]}"